import { AppBar, Tab, Tabs, Toolbar, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'

const Navbar = () => {
  return (
    <React.Fragment>
      <AppBar sx={{background:'	#808080'}}>
        <Toolbar>
          <Typography>LOGO</Typography>
        
      <Tabs  textColor="inherit" marginleft="auto">
      <Tab label="Our Service"/>
      <Tab label="Why Us"/>
      <Tab label="Testimonial"/>
      <Tab label="FAQ"/>
      </Tabs>
      </Toolbar>
      </AppBar>
    </React.Fragment>
  )
}

export default Navbar
